"title": "4824: famine, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4824",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of spiritual hunger arising from a failure to experience the presence and joy of God. Scripture describes such experiences, indicates one ultimate cause to be unbelief and points to ways in which this famine can be relieved.</p>\n<h2>The experience of spiritual famine</h2>\n<h3>God's word is withheld</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:11-Amos8:12\">AMO 8:11–8:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:1\">1SA 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:9\">PSA 74:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:9\">LAM 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:26\">EZK 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:8-Luke23:9\">LUK 23:8–23:9</a></p>\n<h3>God's Spirit is withheld</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:11\">PSA 51:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:33-Ps107:34\">PSA 107:33–107:34</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of spiritual famine</h2>\n<h3>Sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:2\">ISA 59:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Unbelief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:46\">ACT 13:46</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:25-Acts28:28\">ACT 28:25–28:28</a></p>\n<h3>Worldliness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:2\">ISA 55:2</a></p>\n<h3>False beliefs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:19-Isa8:22\">ISA 8:19–8:22</a></p>\n<h3>Self-satisfaction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></strong> <em>It is possible to be well-fed physically but famished spiritually.</em></p>\n<h3>Testing God</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:18-Ps78:19\">PSA 78:18–78:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:29-Ps78:31\">PSA 78:29–78:31</a></p>\n<h3>God testing his servants</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:3\">JOB 23:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:8-Job23:10\">JOB 23:8–23:10</a></p>\n<h2>Consequences of spiritual famine</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual weakness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:81\">PSA 119:81</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:2\">PSA 84:2</a></p>\n<h3>Loss of hope and joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:16\">JOL 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:12\">PSA 51:12</a></p>\n<h2>Relief of spiritual famine</h2>\n<h3>Relief is promised to God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:9\">PSA 107:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:8-Ps85:13\">PSA 85:8–85:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:11\">ISA 58:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:21\">ISA 65:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:13-Amos9:15\">AMO 9:13–9:15</a></p>\n<h3>Relief comes through Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35\">JHN 6:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:1-Isa9:3\">ISA 9:1–9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:53\">LUK 1:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:32-John6:33\">JHN 6:32–6:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:48\">JHN 6:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:50\">JHN 6:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:58\">JHN 6:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:3-1Cor10:4\">1CO 10:3–10:4</a></p>\n<h3>Relief comes by the word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:4\">LUK 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a></p>\n<h3>Relief comes by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17\">ACT 2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28\">JOL 2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:35-Ps107:38\">PSA 107:35–107:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:1-Isa35:10\">ISA 35:1–35:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:3\">ISA 44:3</a></p>\n<h3>Final relief is found in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">REV 7:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:9-Isa49:10\">ISA 49:9–49:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:11\">PSA 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:6\">REV 21:6</a></p>\n<h2>Conditions of relief from spiritual famine</h2>\n<h3>It is offered freely</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1\">ISA 55:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:37\">JHN 7:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:17\">REV 22:17</a></p>\n<h3>It is for those who desire it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:6\">MAT 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:21\">LUK 6:21</a></p>\n<h3>It is for those who pray</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:4-Ps107:9\">PSA 107:4–107:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>It is for those who repent</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:8-Ps81:10\">PSA 81:8–81:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:9-Isa64:10\">ISA 64:9–64:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:1-Hos14:8\">HOS 14:1–14:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:13-Joel2:14\">JOL 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>It is for those who have patience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7\">JAS 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:4-Ps126:6\">PSA 126:4–126:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:1\">ECC 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:35\">JHN 4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16-Jas5:18\">JAS 5:16–5:18</a></p>",
